OL,3,CPatrols stepped up after several
OL,4,Cwindows smashed on South Shields
OL,5,Cseafront
OL,7,FPatrols along South Shields seafront
OL,8,Fhave been stepped up after vandals
OL,9,Fsmashed several of the amphitheatre's
OL,10,Fwindows.
OL,12,FSouth Tyneside Council has confirmed
OL,13,Fit has increased patrols in the area
OL,14,Fand is in the process of replacing the
OL,15,Fpanes damaged by the promenade on
OL,16,FSandhaven Beach.
OL,18,FPolice are investigating after the
OL,19,Fwindows were smashed on consecutive
OL,20,FFridays - 19 January and 26 January.
