OL,7,FCllr Jim Foreman, lead member for
OL,8,Fhousing and community safety, said:
OL,9,F"The Foreshore is a fantastic asset
OL,10,Fwhich makes a significant contribution
OL,11,Fto both our resident and visitor
OL,12,Fexperience.
OL,14,F"It's so disappointing that a minority
OL,15,Fare choosing to carry out these acts
OL,16,Fof vandalism, which spoil our
OL,17,Fseafront, waste valuable officer time
OL,18,Fand ultimately will come down to the
OL,19,Ftaxpayer to rectify.
