OL,7,F"We are working with our partners to
OL,8,Fidentify the offenders and I would ask
OL,9,Fanyone with information to get in
OL,10,Ftouch. They can do this anonymously
OL,11,Fand in confidence."
OL,13,FNorthumbria Police were first called
OL,14,Fto the seafront shortly after 8:30pm
OL,15,Fon Friday 19 January.
OL,17,FThe force said: "It was reported a
OL,18,Fnumber of unknown offenders have
OL,19,Fremoved large blocks of ice from a
OL,20,Fnearby pond and used them to smash the
OL,21,Fglass in the windows of the walkway.
