OL,7,F"Officers attended, however those
OL,8,Fbelieved to have been involved had
OL,9,Falready made off from the scene prior
OL,10,Fto police arrival."
OL,12,FThen on Friday last week (26 January),
OL,13,Fpolice received a call at about 7:35pm
OL,14,Ffollowing reports of ten windows being
OL,15,Fsmashed.
OL,17,FOfficers attended again but those
OL,18,Finvolved had left.
